text: Frederick Hodges (born 8 May 1921) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
